WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:13.000
LLM Studio — a private, multi-model AI workspace with real accounts.

00:13.000 --> 00:22.000
Ask anything — answers stream token-by-token, ChatGPT-style.

00:22.000 --> 00:27.000
Each conversation is private to your account, saved server-side.

00:27.000 --> 00:33.000
Switch models on the fly — one OpenAI-compatible seam over cloud and local providers.

00:33.000 --> 00:41.000
Follow-ups keep the context; a shared key with a fair per-user daily quota keeps it live.

00:41.000 --> 00:45.000
The full SaaS shape: Argon2id auth, per-user tenancy, 31 tests — on a $0 stack.
